author: The Babylon Bee
description:
What if politicians actually told the truth? A concerned citizen visits her congressman hoping for answers—and gets far more honesty than she expected.

Have you noticed that America rocks, but D.C. kinda sucks? That’s why JD Vance, Karoline Leavitt, and millions of Americans have joined the Convention of States movement. To help C-O-S, go to https://conventionofstates.com/bee 

#usa #politics #comedy
title: If Congressmen Were Actually Honest
